k.description: Relative infectivity of mild illness compared to severe and critical illness

theta.description: Proportion of cases that exhibit mild symptoms

q.description: Proportion of severe symptomatic cases who practice self-isolation upon symptom onset

f_i.description: Weight for self-isolation after symptom onset for severe and critical cases

f_a.description: Weight for self-isolation after symptom onset for mild cases

tau_i.description: Average time from symptom onset to self- isolation for severe and critical cases

tau_a.description: Average time from symptom onset to self- isolation for mild cases

delta.description: Average time from symptom onset to hospitalization

gamma.description: Average time from symptom onset to hospitalization

h.description: Proportion of symptomatic patients with severe and critical illness requiring hospital care or ICU

c.description: Proportion of hospitalized cases requiring ICU

p_m.description: Proportion of hospitalized cases that die

mu_h.description: Time from hospitalization (non-ICU) admission to death

psi_h.description: Length of hospital stay before recovery

m_h.description: Weight associated with the model death rate among hospitalized (non-ICU) patients

mu_c.description: Time from ICU admission to death

psi_c.description: Length of ICU stay before recovery

m_c.description: Weight associated with the model death rate among ICU patients
